{"tid":355362,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（法律問題）我咁做會唔會侵犯版權？","createTime":"2017-08-11T08:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T18:52:13.000Z","uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b54fbff40afefc797623a86d7899038bcafaf119","tid":355362,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"如果我未經創作人同意就造叮噹公仔然後賣比人就係侵犯版權<br />\n<br />\n但如果人地比錢我畫叮噹比佢，或者做隻叮噹公仔比佢算唔算侵權？"},{"pid":"829965a8480d9c87280050281f1d67c3a9bd45b0","tid":355362,"uid":94718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"如果並非轉售有版權物品（即2手轉售），在未得版權持有人同意下製造或銷售具版權物品，有可能觸犯<strong>當地</strong>版權條例。<br />\n<br />\n利申：非法撚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://info.legalzoom.com/right-sell-copyrighted-material-22476.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finfo.legalzoom.com%2Fright-sell-copyrighted-material-22476.html&d=pFcolARE4D48kahgiC6wGTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=79facda7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://info.legalzoom.com/right-sell-copyrighted-material-22476.html</a>"},{"pid":"9bce8f93e29fa75a6054d7690de9de6c660dcc00","tid":355362,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"邊個係人地"},{"pid":"0f0de2305b934d011ac16fe9bf167d6571b2bfbd","tid":355362,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:03:57.000Z","msg":"賣野就自己um錢請律師問法律意見啦"},{"pid":"85ba3814d4325a25ab67a17a73e515f2ffedf3c6","tid":355362,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"當觸犯商標權（卡通人物外形都係商標） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebbcb0e47ee7c9ad239d7400c9bd2afe0947623","tid":355362,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣野就自己um錢請律師問法律意見啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n純粹思考緊個問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5586b8793773f11a4c10d1d56a9b358d9f4c8f44","tid":355362,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T18:52:13.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩街邊大把檔口都係咁，<br />\n雖然肯定係犯法，但佢唔會大費周章去告你，<br />\n除非有人督背隻，情況就好似年宵咁"}]}